snippet.title: Gordon Freakman Trailer
snippet.description:
You are Gordon Freakman. You like Crowbars, Black Mesa, Scientists and stuff... 
Gordon Freakman has to destroy all of the Dr. Kleiners because they took over City 69. 
"This is a story one day only of the urban day of sight."
